<div id="artical" class="article">
<h2>穗广日集团连续五名高管被查</h2>
<div class="infos">
<span class="tm">04-21 14:06</span>
<span class="source">来源:<a href="http://www.infzm.com" target="_blank">南方周末</a>
</span>
<span class="author">综合</span>
<div class="shares">
<div class="bdsharebuttonbox" data-tag="share_1">
